WEBVTT

00:07:57.528 --> 00:08:01.061
people flexed muscles that they never
dreamed of using at work.

00:08:02.353 --> 00:08:03.930
People learned new skills,

00:08:03.954 --> 00:08:06.322
they met new people,

00:08:06.346 --> 00:08:09.139
and at the end, somebody
pulled me aside and said,

00:08:09.163 --> 00:08:10.732
"I have to tell you,

00:08:10.756 --> 00:08:13.532
the last few weeks has been
one of the most intense,

00:08:13.556 --> 00:08:16.835
hardest working experiences
of my entire life,

00:08:16.859 --> 00:08:18.900
but not one second of it felt like work."

00:08:20.080 --> 00:08:21.378
And that's the key.

00:08:21.402 --> 00:08:25.112
For those few weeks, people
got to be creators and innovators.

00:08:26.811 --> 00:08:28.478
They had been dreaming of solutions

00:08:28.502 --> 00:08:30.986
to problems that had been
bugging them for years,